SCHEMA: scale/solver_registry_extension.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.scale.solver_registry_extension
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Extend solver registry rows with domain/contract binding metadata.
- Enable structural transition checks for collapse/expand paths.

NON-SEMANTICS:
- Extension fields are structural metadata only.
- Extension fields must not alter solver numerical method definitions.

REQUIRED SHAPE (per solver row):
- domain_ids: [id]
- contract_ids: [id]
- resolution_tags: [tag]
- cost_class: tag
- transition_support: [tag]
- refusal_codes: [id]

INVARIANTS:
- Every solver row MUST bind to at least one domain and contract ID.
- transition_support must explicitly declare supported directions.
- Unsupported transition requests must deterministically refuse.

MIGRATION:
- New transition dimensions require schema update and validator changes.
